{"tid":2505143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前高官何志平北角熟食中心宴客 9人同枱疑違限聚令","createTime":"2021-04-26T11:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T11:46:37.000Z","uid":251258,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"35132b324143b022e5924cf3d4de0ffe3f6b37cb","tid":2505143,"uid":251258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T11:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVbvVuxtC8aEQ93wejaaGE1xL97KAau4qA4qmpRo8iyyH?filename=geZfPBY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgeZfPBY.png&h=bfdb5b50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年71歲、本港前民政事務局局長何志平，2019年在美國被控貪污及洗黑錢賄賂案罪成，太太胡慧中在法庭交上親撰的求情信，形容丈夫是「飽學之士，心地善良而寬厚，是真心實意的正人君子。」最終獲判入獄3年、罰款40萬美金。何志平去年中出獄後，被遣送返港。經過近10個月養尊處優，現差不多回復入獄前的身形。昨晚他跟太太在北角招呼友人食飯飲酒，不過同枱共9人兼冇間隔，疑違反限聚令。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">美國嘅監都坐過啦驚閪咩</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919a45a63acd01030c6a04e6271d0e40610a6c32","tid":2505143,"uid":251258,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T11:27:44.000Z","msg":"應該改個標題做<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">前監躉何志平</span></span>"},{"pid":"e6cacb7c82ff25094d03c2f85229fdd251f2ba31","tid":2505143,"uid":80314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T11:32:37.000Z","msg":"應該改個標題做<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">釋囚人士何志平</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5ef53dbf2d7abc99fdbf2d36584a242c2fcd7795","tid":2505143,"uid":393145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T11:33:22.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">現差不多回復入獄前的身形</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4eb8248a20bfae2fdd2cddc9c3be413b5a48d53","tid":2505143,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim